                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 footer-box">
                    <p><b>CONTACT US</b></p>
                    <P><i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>Bulevardi Zogu I, Tirana</P>
                    <P><i class="fa fa-phone"></i>+1 0123456789</P>
                    <P><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i>abc@gmail.com</P>

                </div>
